{0 Forester: A language for scientific hypertext}

{1 Introduction}

Forester is a compiled markup language for authoring scientific hypertext. This documentation is intended to give an overview of forester internals for people interested in contributing to the project.

{1 Codebase overview}

The code is organized into several libraries:

{!modules:
  Forester_prelude
  Forester_core
  Forester_compiler
  Forester_frontend
  Forester_lsp}
